trans-unit.source: Defines the binding element used to create a Peer Name Resolution Protocol (PNRP) peer resolver.
trans-unit.target: Define o elemento de associação usado para criar um resolvedor de pares de resolução protocolo PNRP (Peer Name).

trans-unit.source: To create a peer resolver from an instance of this class, call <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.PnrpPeerResolverBindingElement.CreatePeerResolver%2A> after the instance has been constructed.
trans-unit.target: Para criar um resolvedor de pares de uma instância dessa classe, chame <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.PnrpPeerResolverBindingElement.CreatePeerResolver%2A>depois que a instância foi construída.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.PnrpPeerResolverBindingElement.CreatePeerResolver%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new default instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.PnrpPeerResolverBindingElement"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância padrão do <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.PnrpPeerResolverBindingElement"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.PnrpPeerResolverBindingElement"></xref> class with the provided peer referral policy.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.PnrpPeerResolverBindingElement"> </xref> classe com a diretiva de referência de ponto a ponto fornecido.

trans-unit.source: <xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerReferralPolicy"></xref> that specifies the referral policy for this resolver.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.ServiceModel.PeerResolvers.PeerReferralPolicy"></xref>que especifica a diretiva de referência para esse resolvedor.
